  "content": "ar(--bg-card); color: var(--text-secondary);\">gRPC &bull; per-model routing</td>\n      <td style=\"padding: 18px 20px; font-size: 17px; font-weight: 700; background: var(--bg-card); color: var(--accent-amber);\">Fallback-with-signal</td>\n    </tr>\n  </table>\n  <div class=\"terminal\" style=\"font-size: 14px;\">\n    <span class=\"comment\"># Route each model to its own backend</span><br>\n    <span class=\"prompt\">$ </span><span class=\"cmd\">corvia inference reload \\</span><br>\n    <span class=\"cmd\">&nbsp;&nbsp;--model nomic-embed-text-v1.5 --backend </span><span class=\"highlight-val\">openvino</span><br><br>\n    <span class=\"prompt\">$ </span><span class=\"cmd\">corvia inference reload \\</span><br>\n    <span class=\"cmd\">&nbsp;&nbsp;--model llama3.2 --backend </span><span class=\"highlight-val\">cuda</span>\n  </div>\n\n  <div class=\"insight-box\">\n    <p>Each model gets its own backend. All Rust. All local. No API keys.</p>\n  </div>\n\n  <div class=\"flex-grow\"></div>\n  <div class=\"author-tag\">Lim Chun Zhe</div>\n  <div class=\"slide-number\">07 / 08</div>\n</div>\n\n<!-- SLIDE 8: TAKEAWAYS — fewer items, bigger text -->\n<div class=\"slide\" style=\"background: linear-gradient(160deg, #0f172a 0%, #1a2332 50%, #0f172a 100%);\">\n  <div class=\"slide-label\">Takeaways</div>\n  <div class=\"slide-title\" style=\"margin-bottom: 48px;\">\n    What I Learned<br>\n    <span class=\"highlight-green\">This Week</span>\n  </div>\n\n  <div style=\"display: flex; flex-direction: column; gap: 32px;\">\n    <div style=\"display: flex; align-items: center; gap: 24px;\">\n      <div style=\"width: 80px; height: 80px; border-radius: 50%; background: rgba(6, 182, 212, 0.15); display: flex; align-items: center; justify-content: center; font-size: 40px; flex-shrink: 0;\">&#9889;</div>\n      <div>\n        <div style=\"font-size: 24px; font-weight: 800; margin-bottom: 6px;\">Your iGPU is free compute.</div>\n        <div style=\"font-size: 17px; color: var(--text-secondary);\">Split workloads instead of fighting for one GPU.</div>\n      </div>\n    </div>\n\n    <div class=\"divider\" style=\"margin: 0;\"></div>",
